<h2>🌾 About Agriculture</h2>

<p style="line-height:1.8;">
Agriculture is the backbone of the economy and focuses on crop production, livestock management, food technology, and sustainable farming. Modern agriculture combines science, technology, and innovation to improve food production and protect natural resources.
